reviews.text: Very cool place for kids.
classy place with kids and friendly staff
Great place. Our daughter love it.

There is a $40k joining fee, so you can't just go unless you are with a member.
Nice indoor playground for little kids and a cool rooftop with chairs, kids toys and some fun ways to get a little wet.
Very reasonably priced food (depending on how you think about the membership fee) and good.  Great breakfast and cofee.

Members only club, members can bring guest.  This place is like a giant playpen for adults and their kids.  Decent food from both adult and children's menu.  There's a ball pool here which is hard to find now a days due to all the children infections around.  I see cleaning lady's constantly whiping down the place and toys.
